            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
