    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the ragù has thickened, add your <strong>soft cheese </strong>and <strong>drained tortiglioni</strong> to the pan with a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and stir until the sauce coats the pasta – this is your <strong>creamy lean pork and mushroom tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
